---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Availability from "../components/Availability.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Robin van Baalen" description="About Robin van Baalen — software engineer, consultant, and builder with almost two decades of experience.">
  <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight text-primary">About</h1>
  <div class="max-w-xl space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      I'm Robin van Baalen. I've been building software for almost twenty years,
      across roles from developer to architect to consultant. But titles aren't
      really the point.
    </p>
    <p>
      The point is that I genuinely love this. I follow the news obsessively, try
      every new tool that comes out, and care deeply about the craft of making
      software that works well. From AI-assisted development to system architecture,
      from team dynamics to developer tooling... if it's happening in our industry,
      I'm probably already playing with it.
    </p>
    <p>
      I write about what I learn here and open-source what I build. Most of my
      packages are zero-dependency utilities that solve one problem well.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're working through a tricky architecture decision, curious what AI
      can actually do for your team right now, or just want to bounce ideas off
      someone who's seen a lot of codebases... I'd love to hear from you. No pitch,
      no pressure. You'll walk away with something useful.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8">
    <Availability />
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8">
    <a
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-accent px-6 py-3 font-sans text-[16px] font-medium text-[var(--color-base)] transition-[background,transform,box-shadow] duration-150 hover:bg-accent-bright hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-[0_4px_12px_var(--color-accent-glow)] active:translate-y-0"
    >
      <i class="ph ph-coffee" aria-hidden="true" />
      Let's talk
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
